flowchart TD
    A(Start Solver) --> B{Rotation Mode?}
    B -->|Sequential| C(Sequential Rotation Loop)
    B -->|Parallel| D(Thread Loop)

    %% Sequential Mode
    C --> E[Evaluate All Rotations]
    E --> F{Solution Found?}
    F -->|Yes| G(Return Solution)
    F -->|No| H(End)

    %% Parallel Mode
    D --> I[Create Worker Threads]
    I --> J[Distribute Rotations to Threads]
    J --> K[Thread Solves Rotation]
    K --> L{Solution Found?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Set Result and Stop Others]
    L -->|No| D
    M --> G

    G --> H(End)
